{
  "stem": "14737.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "From a small town, I cannot do nothing, but here there are organizations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There are the American consul.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the meantime, I left my papers to transfer from Prague, which I have an affidavit, to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And yeah, they transferred that to an account to the consul.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they have the papers, but wait for the quota.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So at least I have some number here to wait.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had a paper in the American consul-- well, my line will come and my--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no work, nothing in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in this, why do I go to the Jewish headquarters?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, to go for me to a hotel, I have no money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there are places.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is a woman has an apartment of two or three rooms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In one room she has-- what do you call?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Occupants, sleepers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she has six, eight beds and so she rents you a bed for a nominal sum.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it's not so bad what-- and to eat, there's also-- there are places, there are cheap places.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I find myself also a job there in the Jewish hospital, as a worker, not as a doctor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I, myself, and work a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But here comes the story. 1940, as the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Germans occupied [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Poland, many Polish Jews fled to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many fled to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As you know, they are divided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not going to tell you about story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But many fled there, Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, they came in different place, different towns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Here in Budapest, in those places, there are-- it was around May-- May, June, 1940.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There are raids at night, very many raids, and this-- where Jews live in this place, and they're looking for spies.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
